title: Relationships (Skit)
lyrics: Yeah. Relationships, there's so many types, but some of the common ones are business relationships, friendship relationships, and especially love relationships. We all go through that, and if you haven't, you will one day. But there's one that really really stands out when it comes to relationships. The building of it. And that's what we call the flirt. Now let me explain it real quick to you. Some people got skills at flirtin'. Some people don't. Here's an example
